    <summary>Configure GTK theme colors</summary>
    <description>
        <p>
        The tool allows anyone to change some basic elements of a GTK theme
        easily (both GTK2 and GTK3) with a simple interface.
        </p>
        <p>Features:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Customize selection background color</li>
            <li>Customize Xfce panel, Gnome panel and Unity panel</li>
            <li>Customize menu colors</li>
        </ul>
    </description>
